#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="39"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.3.4.3"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1171"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.3.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññatarā itthī navāvutaṃ kambalaṃ pārutā hoti."
msgstr ""
"At one time a certain woman was wearing a newly woven upper robe of wool."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.3.2"
msgid "Aññataro bhikkhu sāratto taṃ itthiṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "A monk, being lustful, said to her,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.3.3"
msgid "“ākiṇṇalomaṃ kho te, bhaginī”ti."
msgstr "“Sister, is that thick hair yours?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.3.4"
msgid "Sā na paṭivijāni."
msgstr "She did not understand and said,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.3.5"
msgid "“Āmāyya, navāvuto kambalo”ti."
msgstr "“Yes, Venerable, it’s a newly woven upper robe of wool.”"

