#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="42"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.3.4.6"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1174"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.131"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.6.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññatarā itthī khettaṃ vapāpetvā āgacchati."
msgstr "At one time a woman was returning after having had a field sown."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.6.2"
msgid "Aññataro bhikkhu sāratto taṃ itthiṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "A monk, being lustful, said to her,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.6.3"
msgid "“vāpitaṃ kho te, bhaginī”ti?"
msgstr "“Have you sown, Sister?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.6.4"
msgid "Sā na paṭivijāni."
msgstr "She did not understand and said,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.6.5"
msgid "“Āmāyya, no ca kho paṭivuttan”ti."
msgstr "“Yes, Venerable, but the furrow is not yet closed.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.6.6"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.6.7"
msgid "“anāpatti, bhikkhu, saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa;"
msgstr "“There’s no offense entailing suspension,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.6.8"
msgid "āpatti dukkaṭassā”ti."
msgstr "but there’s an offense of wrong conduct.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.6.9"
msgid "(6)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="43"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.3.4.7"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1175"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.7.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu paribbājikaṃ paṭipathe passitvā "
"sāratto taṃ paribbājikaṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr ""
"At one time a monk saw a female wanderer coming in the opposite direction, "
"and being lustful he said to her,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.7.2"
msgid "“kacci, bhagini, maggo saṃsīdatī”ti?"
msgstr "“Sister, I hope the path has an end?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.7.3"
msgid "Sā na paṭivijāni."
msgstr "She did not understand and said,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.7.4"
msgid "“Āma, bhikkhu, paṭipajjissasī”ti."
msgstr "“Yes, just keep going.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.7.5"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.7.6"
msgid "“anāpatti, bhikkhu, saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa;"
msgstr "“There’s no offense entailing suspension,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.7.7"
msgid "āpatti thullaccayassā”ti."
msgstr "but there’s a serious offense.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.7.8"
msgid "(7)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="44"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.3.4.8"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1176"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.8.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu sāratto aññataraṃ itthiṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "At one time a monk, being lustful, said to a woman,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.8.2"
msgid "“saddhāsi tvaṃ, bhagini."
msgstr "“You have confidence, Sister,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.8.3"
msgid "Api ca yaṃ sāmikassa desi taṃ nāmhākaṃ desī”ti."
msgstr "but you don’t give us what you give your husband.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.8.4"
msgid "“Kiṃ, bhante”ti?"
msgstr "“What’s that, Venerable?”"

#. </p><p><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.221"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.8.5"
msgid "“Methunadhamman”ti."
msgstr "“Sexual intercourse.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.8.6"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.8.7"
msgid "“āpattiṃ tvaṃ, bhikkhu, āpanno saṃghādisesan”ti."
msgstr "“There’s an offense entailing suspension.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.8.8"
msgid "(8)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="45"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.3.4.9"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1177"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.9.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu sāratto aññataraṃ itthiṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "At one time a monk, being lustful, said to a woman,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.9.2"
msgid "“saddhāsi tvaṃ, bhagini."
msgstr "“You have confidence, Sister,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.9.3"
msgid "Api ca yaṃ aggadānaṃ taṃ nāmhākaṃ desī”ti."
msgstr "yet you don’t give us the highest gift.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.9.4"
msgid "“Kiṃ, bhante, aggadānan”ti?"
msgstr "“What’s the highest gift, Venerable?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.9.5"
msgid "“Methunadhamman”ti."
msgstr "“Sexual intercourse.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.9.6"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.9.7"
msgid "“āpattiṃ tvaṃ, bhikkhu, āpanno saṃghādisesan”ti."
msgstr "“There’s an offense entailing suspension.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.9.8"
msgid "(9)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="46"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.3.4.10"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1178"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.10.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññatarā itthī kammaṃ karoti."
msgstr "At one time a woman was doing some work."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.10.2"
msgid "Aññataro bhikkhu sāratto taṃ itthiṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "A monk, being lustful, said to her,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.10.3"
msgid "“tiṭṭha, bhagini, ahaṃ karissāmī”ti … pe …"
msgstr "“Stand, Sister, I’ll work.” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.10.4"
msgid "nisīda, bhagini, ahaṃ karissāmī”ti … pe …"
msgstr "“Sit, Sister, I’ll work.” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.10.5"
msgid "nipajja, bhagini, ahaṃ karissāmī”ti."
msgstr "“Lie down, Sister, I’ll work.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.10.6"
msgid "Sā na paṭivijāni."
msgstr "She did not understand."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.10.7"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.10.8"
msgid "“anāpatti, bhikkhu, saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa;"
msgstr "“There’s no offense entailing suspension,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.10.9"
msgid "āpatti dukkaṭassā”ti."
msgstr "but there’s an offense of wrong conduct.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.10.10"
msgid "(10–‍12)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="47"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1179"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss3:pts-cs4.10.11"
msgid "Duṭṭhul­la­vācā­sikkhā­padaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ tatiyaṃ."
msgstr "The third rule, the training rule on lewd speech, is finished."

